humb";s:123:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTnDmvZqgFN6enFfdwRkRClB0TyvKn8nKvojuNOOy9elWoxhJuWgGU1zXDsdfyIA-DVOzA";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:360;s:6:"height";i:480;s:6:"source";s:48:"https://cz.pinterest.com/pin/406027722640098569/";s:6:"domain";s:16:"cz.pinterest.com";}i:20;a:11:{s:7:"keyword";s:30:"chair yoga for elderly youtube";s:4:"slug";s:30:"chair-yoga-for-elderly-youtube";s:5:"title";s:106:"1 Hour Chair Yoga Class Reach Bend Move But Most Importantly Breathe Chair Yoga Yoga Help Yoga For Seniors";s:3:"alt";s:106:"1 hour chair yoga class reach bend move but most importantly breathe chair yoga yoga help yoga for seniors";s:3:"url";s:76:"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/65/3e/8e/653e8e0f137121294258458ae7055a14.jpg";s:5:"thumb";s:90:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRC2SY68eaN5rB2VaOL918miN_emEGETFAcFA";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:360;s:6:"height";i:480;s:6:"source";s:49:"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/512495632591636563/";s:6:"domain";s:17:"www.pinterest.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:55:{i:0;s:54:"10 Minutes Gentle Chair Yoga For Seniors And Desk Job.";i:1;s:118:"Yoga is an excellent way for older adults to loosen and stretch painful muscles reduce stress and improve circulation.";i:2;s:99:"It also reduces anxiety helps lower blood pressure protects joints and builds strength and balance.";i:3;s:95:"We found a fantastic 30 minute routine of gentle chair yoga for seniors thats free to watch on.";i:4;s:118:"Yoga is an excellent way for older adults to loosen and stretch painful muscles reduce stress and improve circulation.";i:5;s:99:"It also reduces anxiety helps lower blood pressure protects joints and builds strength and balance.";i:6;s:103:"We found a fantastic 30 minute routine of gentle chair yoga for seniors thats free to watch on YouTube.";i:7;s:88:"Chair yoga is a great way for older adults to get the wonderful health benefits of yoga.";i:8;s:31:"Chair yoga for elderly youtube.";i:9;s:101:"Staying seated means that even frail seniors or those who arent flexible can safely do the exercises.";i:10;s:112:"This sequence will benefit anyone who prefers to do yoga in a chair such as seniors or those in a chair at work.";i:11;s:61:"Nov 3 2016 - Explore Sleighs board YouTube yoga on Pinterest.";i:12;s:54:"See more ideas about yoga chair yoga yoga for seniors.";i:13;s:35:"Apr 8 2019 - Welcome to chair yoga.";i:14;s:89:"Come join our senior yoga group where you can move stretch and relax the gentle yoga way.";i:15;s:44:"This is a one hour live recording of Jan Ho.";i:16;s:23:"Chair Yoga for Seniors.";i:17;s:134:"7 Poses To Try Whether youre heading to a yoga class or trying some poses out at home these yoga exercises are a great place to start.";i:18;s:163:"We begin with simple exercises and work up to more advanced poses offering modifications along the way to help increase the stretch or reduce the difficulty level.";i:19;s:71:"Chair yoga is a mild form of exercise but an effective one nonetheless.";i:20;s:223:"Most American adults are overweight a problem that dramatically worsens with ageJumping right into an exercise regimen at an advanced age is asking for trouble primarily if you havent engaged in physical training for years.";i:21;s:128:"Remember chair yoga isnt just for seniors or beginners its a great way to add a little movement into an otherwise sedentary day.";i:22;s:128:"Something is better than nothing and if you work at a desk this can be a great way to recenter after all those conference calls.";i:23;s:58:"If you want more videos then check out my YouTube channel.";i:24;s:15:"There are many.";i:25;s:48:"Chair Yoga - Yoga For Seniors Yoga With Adriene.";i:26;s:115:"Chair Yoga invites you to find mobility in a way that is soft and gentle but also really supportive and beneficial.";i:27;s:102:"This 17 min practice invites awareness and integrity into the body specifically the line of the spine.";i:28;s:72:"Activate the muscles that help you find length up through the spine for.";i:29;s:78:"Look after your balance with Chair Yoga online every Tuesday Thursday morning.";i:30;s:85:"This is video 3 of 3 videos on Yoga for Beginners which is a great class for seniors.";i:31;s:63:"A great introduction to some of the more common posses in Yoga.";i:32;s:68:"We take it super slow with just enough explanation but not too much.";i:33;s:62:"We cover poses such as gate pose Warrior 1 pose and tree pose.";i:34;s:62:"If you havent done yoga before try out Videos 1 and 2 as well.";i:35;s:161:"Unlike high-impact exercise like running lifting weights and plyometrics chair yoga is easy on your joints and may serve as a gateway to other forms of exercise.";i:36;s:117:"Chair yoga is a beneficial form of yoga for any fitness level from active seniors to those recovering from an injury.";i:37;s:32:"Adaptive Chair Yoga for Seniors.";i:38;s:116:"In addition to the various types of yoga adaptive practices help seniors with even very limited mobility to do yoga.";i:39;s:32:"Adaptive yoga practices include.";i:40;s:103:"Chair Yoga Ideal for those who cannot stand for long periods of time or who cannot work on a floor mat.";i:41;s:123:"Sharon Hong Maurmann who has taught our Senior Center yoga classes since 2014 now teaches chair-based yoga classes on Zoom.";i:42;s:152:"Classes are offered on an optional donation basis with a portion of class fees to benefit South Sound Senior Services and the Thurston County Food Bank.";i:43;s:112:"Classes are chair-based with standing and mat options as well as the option to stay seated for the entire class.";i:44;s:36:"A Visionary in Aging Well with Yoga.";i:45;s:131:"Founded in 2003 Sherrys video production company YogaJP brought Gentle Senior and Chair Yoga into the mainstream of the Yoga world.";i:46;s:122:"Her Yoga Videos serve the Boomers and Seniors with Yoga that is accessible and designed especially for their health needs.";i:47;s:26:"Her YogaVistaTV streaming.";i:48;s:65:"Chair yoga is great for seniors or beginners who are new to yoga.";i:49;s:145:"This video features some favorite chair yoga exercises for seniors or people with limited range of motion but everyone can enjoy these exercises.";i:50;s:124:"Its also perfect if you have injuries or want to know how you can use a chair to stretch in the airport office or on the go.";i:51;s:55:"Chair yoga is simply adapting yoga asanas with a chair.";i:52;s:144:"The chair makes yoga postures accessible to students by offering additional support and is a great way to help improve strength and flexibility.";i:53;s:55:"To do chair yoga your need a sturdy chair with no arms.";i:54;s:85:"The height of the chair depends on your body but you want to either be able to touch.";}}